If you have any problem when you use this skill, you can contact us with email : office@4ddoors.com
4Dconnect products will help you control home appliance nice and easy.
After connecting Alexa to your 4Dconnect products in a few simple steps:
1. Download our “4Dconnect” app in app market then register an account (or log in directly if you already have an account);
2. Configure our devices in “4Dconnect” app and change appropriate name for your devices;
3. Enable “4Dconnect” skill on Alexa app, you'll be navigated to the login page, follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
4. Tell Echo "Alexa, discover my devices". Wait for Echo to say “Search complete”;
5. Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, open the Garage Door”
“Alexa, close the Garage Door”
